{
  "chapter": 43,
  "chapter_summary": "钱卓据峡谷高处以弩箭巨石困杀丐帮，凌龙强攻受重伤，丐帮群豪仍前仆后继。仇恕救下凌龙后压住众人冲动，命削竹木为兵，并受凌龙托付暂代帮主指挥突围。多次攻势失败后，他决定拂晓独闯，慕容惜生在死生关头表露真情。端木方正、朱白羽、石磷、华山银鹤从峡谷外来援，四剑齐攻一度打开局面。华山银鹤因杀父旧仇迟疑，反致攻势败退，仇恕却冒险救他，促成二人化解先人仇恨。众人精神稍振，钱卓却冷声宣告守势已变，危机未解。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_qian_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "钱卓",
      "listener": "char_ling_long",
      "text": "老匹夫，你这是找死！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "你……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "慕容惜生",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "冲吧！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_long",
      "speaker_name": "凌龙",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "你们不要管我，冲，冲，和他们拼了！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gai_bang_qun_hao",
      "speaker_name": "丐帮群豪",
      "listener": "char_ling_long",
      "text": "冲呀，冲上去为帮主复仇！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_gai_bang_qun_hao",
      "text": "且慢！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gai_bang_di_zi",
      "speaker_name": "丐帮弟子",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "仇公子还有什么话说？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_gai_bang_qun_hao",
      "text": "你等身无防身之物，亦无攻敌计划，如此冲上去，哪里是与敌人拼命，只不过是送死罢了。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gai_bang_di_zi",
      "speaker_name": "丐帮弟子",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "纵是送死，又有什么办法？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_gai_bang_qun_hao",
      "text": "先歇息片刻，设法寻找竹木，编成盾牌，再寻些刀剑，攻敌防身，到那时再去拼命，也不算迟。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gai_bang_di_zi",
      "speaker_name": "丐帮弟子",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "刀剑俱已和尸身一齐埋下去了，那时弟兄们都已心灰意冷，不愿争杀，哪知道……竟发生此变！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_gai_bang_qun_hao",
      "text": "纵无刀剑，也要削竹为剑，削木成刀，总比赤手空拳好些，弟兄们，快去分头做事！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "慕容惜生",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "拔不得的，此地既无伤药，亦无清水，你拔下了箭，只怕伤势溃烂，凌帮主这条手臂，就……就……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_ling_long",
      "text": "凌帮主，在下先前曾夸下海口，总希望不要丐帮为助，这些话……这些话帮主你还记得么？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_long",
      "speaker_name": "凌龙",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "那日我揭穿了你的行径，你自然难免有些怒气！",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_ling_long",
      "text": "又有谁知道，在下此刻正是孤立无助时，却只有丐帮的弟兄，为我援手，为我拼命，为我——",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "慕容惜生",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "这种话你以后不要再说，也就是了……",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gai_bang_di_zi",
      "speaker_name": "丐帮弟子",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "仇公子，竹剑虽轻，却是我家全部弟兄一点心意！\n\n但望仇公子能以此竹剑，为帮主复仇！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_gai_bang_di_zi",
      "text": "多谢你们弟兄的好意。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gai_bang_di_zi",
      "speaker_name": "丐帮弟子",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "此刻弟兄们都已歇息好了，可以寻来的竹木，也都已寻来，只要公子一声令下，弟兄们立刻动手！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_ling_long",
      "text": "在下一介少年，怎敢号令丐帮的弟兄……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_long",
      "speaker_name": "凌龙",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "事值非常，我也受了重伤，你难道还不肯暂代帮主之位，指挥丐帮弟兄，共同杀开血路？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_ling_long",
      "text": "既然如此，在下只有从命！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_gai_bang_qun_hao",
      "text": "由首至尾，先报数一遍。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gai_bang_di_zi",
      "speaker_name": "丐帮弟子",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "一！",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_gai_bang_qun_hao",
      "text": "由头至尾，接着不断地报下去，让对方猜不出我等人数。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 143,
      "line_end": 145
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qian_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "钱卓",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "你这疑兵之计，瞒得过别人，却瞒不过我的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 151,
      "line_end": 153
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qian_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "钱卓",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "你若少报些人，我反而相信，但你却报得太多了些！",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 155,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "想不到灵蛇门下，竟有这样一个角色。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 159,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_gai_bang_qun_hao",
      "text": "一百四十七人，十人一队，分成十四队，余下的七人，留在这里，看护着帮主的伤势！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 163,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_long",
      "speaker_name": "凌龙",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "一人已足够，其余的却跟着仇公子去！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_gai_bang_qun_hao",
      "text": "十四队人，分向而攻，切莫集在一起！",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 171,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_gai_bang_qun_hao",
      "text": "随我来！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 173,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ling_long",
      "speaker_name": "凌龙",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "仇公子，慕容姑娘……",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_gai_bang_qun_hao",
      "text": "凌帮主只是愤怒过度，不妨事的。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gai_bang_di_zi",
      "speaker_name": "丐帮弟子",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "仇公子，与其坐守而死，不如再决一死战，纵有一人能逃脱此间，将来也有复仇之望，否则——",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_gai_bang_qun_hao",
      "text": "拂晓之际，对方必定防守较疏，那时我自当再拼一次，你们只管好生歇息，不要乱想……",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gai_bang_di_zi",
      "speaker_name": "丐帮弟子",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "仇公子之意，是要我们都留在这里，单独去闯么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_gai_bang_di_zi",
      "text": "不错！你们去了，也是白白送死，我单独去试，还可能成功，只要我一冲将上去。\n\n便可扰乱他们的放箭，那时你们冲上去的机会，也就多了。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gai_bang_di_zi",
      "speaker_name": "丐帮弟子",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "如是公子冲不上去，又当如何？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_gai_bang_di_zi",
      "text": "若是冲不上去，他们见我死了，也就不会再十分难为你们，防守必定松懈，甚至撤兵而退！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gai_bang_qun_hao",
      "speaker_name": "丐帮群豪",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "要冲就一齐冲，我们怎能眼见——",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_gai_bang_qun_hao",
      "text": "住口！此刻我暂代帮主之位，令出如山，你们竟敢违抗帮主之命么？\n\n快去寻地稍息，拂晓已将近了！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "text": "只是……只是我连累了你了……",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_rong_xi_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "慕容惜生",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "我能和你死在一起，已算幸福得很……",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_gu_wai_lai_ren",
      "speaker_name": "峡谷外来人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "上面的是什么人，丐帮的集会，可是在这里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_mu_fang_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "另一人",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "石磷、朱白羽、华山银鹤前来拜访！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_gai_bang_qun_hao",
      "text": "这是端木方正的声音，快过去！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qian_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "钱卓",
      "listener": "char_duan_mu_fang_zheng",
      "text": "此路已被封死，妄上一步，立有惨死之祸！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhu_bai_yu",
      "speaker_name": "朱白羽",
      "listener": "char_qian_zhuo",
      "text": "放屁！大爷们要来便来，要去便去，谁敢拦阻？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_duan_mu_fang_zheng",
      "text": "端木兄、弟仇恕，被困于此！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_mu_fang_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "端木方正",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "仇恕，是你？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_duan_mu_fang_zheng",
      "text": "但望端木兄助我一臂之力——",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_mu_fang_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "端木方正",
      "listener": "char_chou_shu",
      "text": "好！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qian_zhuo",
      "speaker_name": "钱卓",
      "listener": "char_qian_zhuo_shou_xia",
      "text": "后退者死！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": "char_hua_shan_yin_he",
      "text": "退下！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chou_shu",
      "speaker_name": "仇恕",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "去！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_shan_yin_he",
      "speaker_name": "华山银鹤",
      "listener": "char_duan_mu_fang_zheng",
      "text": "贫道对不起各位！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 43,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_mu_fang_zheng",
      "speaker_name": "端木方正",
      "listener": "char_hua_shan_yin_he",
